spark2 (2.4.3-bin-hadoop2.6-1) buster-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * Spark 2.4.3 release
  * Include python 'assembly' zip files for python3.5 and python3.7
    to ease upgrade testing.

 -- Andrew Otto (WMF) <otto@wikimedia.org>  Mon, 26 Aug 2019 20:11:03 +0000

spark2 (2.3.1-bin-hadoop2.6-4) buster-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * Includes all python dependencies for both python 3.5 and 3.7
  * Removes spark user and group on apt-get purge
  * Versions spark assembly.zip in usr/lib/spark2/
  * No longer installs spark assembly.zip in HDFS. This must be done
    manually after install.

 -- Andrew Otto <otto@wikimedia.org>  Tue, 06 Aug 2019 21:29:24 +0000

