    See also: https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/T202812
  * Default to python3 and ipython3 for pyspark.

 -- Andrew Otto (WMF) <otto@wikimedia.org>  Thu, 28 Aug 2018 19:56:42 +0000

spark2 (2.3.1-bin-hadoop2.6-2~stretch1) stretch-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * Added versionless symlink for py4j so users of this package don't need to
    update PYTHONPATHs if they launch pyspark without using the shell wrapper
    (e.g. Jupyter Notebook iPython kernel).

